@RehanSaeed it's your issue linked in the original description of this above :-)

We won't support the same config element (`Logging`) as in the example - there are very few other sections that would overlap with the Microsoft one - but the same style would be a winner under `Serilog`.

We have some basic JSON config support for RC1 here, currently being updated to RC2: https://github.com/serilog/serilog-settings-configuration
